## Step 1: Identify initial current liabilities
First, I need to examine the initial balances at 2023-12-31 to see if there are any current liabilities already recognized.

Looking at the initial entries (Initial20231231001), I don't see any explicit current liabilities. The initial entries show:

There are no initial current liabilities mentioned, so the initial value is 0.00.
